The '''Senatorial speeder barn''' was a division of the [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]-based [[Senate apartment complex/Legends|Senate Apartment Complex]]. Within the barn, different [[Senator/Legends|senators]] housed stored their personal [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeders]] and other vehicles the politicians utilized in navigating the large city-[[Planet/Legends|planet]].

Senator [[Simon Greyshade/Legends|Simon Greyshade]] was known to have stored his personal craft, the [[XJ-6 airspeeder/Legends|XJ-6 airspeeder]], in this speeder barn. After a failed assassination attempt on [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala's]] life, [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] rushed into the barn and hot-wired Greyshade's vehicle to chase assassin [[Zam Wesell/Legends|Zam Wesell]] and rescue his [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]]. After the ensuing chase and subsequent death of the assassin, the XJ-6 was stealthily moved back into its spot in the Senatorial speeder barn by the Jedi, much to the dismay of the local Coruscant officials, who were forced to write it off as a "rookie error".

